  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle the AP &amp; AR accounts.</li>\n  <li>Assist with basic accounting functions,processing invoices and managing accounts payable and receivable.</li>\n  <li>Manage the monthly cash book, including payment vouchers, cash vouchers, and showroom vouchers.</li>\n  <li>Verify and process staff claims.</li>\n  <li>Post customer payments.</li>\n  <li>Perform other assigned ad hoc duties as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
